---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
	<section>
		<h1>Projects</h1>
		<p>These are learning projects I've built while exploring web development and digital training.</p>

		<div class="project-card">
			<h2>Portfolio Website</h2>
			<p>
				A personal website built with Astro and deployed to Cloudflare Pages. This is the project you're viewing now.
			</p>
			<a href="https://github.com/woodoo11/ms-portfolio" target="_blank">View on GitHub</a>
		</div>

		<div class="project-card">
			<h2>SAP Learning Materials</h2>
			<p>
				Training content and learning solutions for SAP Enable Now, focused on improving user adoption and knowledge retention.
			</p>
			<a href="https://github.com/woodoo11" target="_blank">View my GitHub</a>
		</div>

		<div class="project-card">
			<h2>Learning Notes</h2>
			<p>
				Ongoing notes and small experiments documenting what I'm learning in web development, Git, and deployment.
			</p>
			<a href="https://github.com/woodoo11" target="_blank">View my GitHub</a>
		</div>
	</section>

	<style>
		section {
			background: white;
			border-radius: 16px;
			padding: 2rem;
			box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.05);
		}

		h1 {
			font-size: 2.5rem;
			margin-bottom: 1rem;
		}

		p {
			font-size: 1.05rem;
			line-height: 1.8;
		}

		.project-card {
			margin-top: 1.5rem;
			padding: 1.5rem;
			border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
			border-radius: 12px;
		}

		.project-card h2 {
			margin-top: 0;
		}

		.project-card a {
			display: inline-block;
			margin-top: 1rem;
			color: #2563eb;
			text-decoration: none;
		}

		.project-card a:hover {
			text-decoration: underline;
		}
	</style>
